<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erfurt</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass der verstorbene Hans von Goßerstetten, Bürger zu Erfurt, eine große Menge Waid im Waidhaus zu Nürnberg hinterlassen hat, die man nur einem Berechtigten aushändigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_527" id="263r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_527_r1l16">Erfford </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_527_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Hanſen ſeligen / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l18">Berlds ſeins prüders von <expan>Goſʒerſtete<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>mitburge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l19">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd laſſen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> vviſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l21">daʒ vvir nichts hie erfaren <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> / das der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Hans von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l22"><expan>Goſʒerſtete<ex>n</ex></expan> ſelig <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> hie gelaſſen hab / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> etvvieuil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l23">vvaits der hie auf dem vveithauſe ligt / vnd den mag auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l24"> <expan>nyemand<ex>en</ex></expan> hie bekümern noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pieten</expan> / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> der 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſelb </del> wait 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l28">
<del rend="strikethrough">auch geleite </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_527_line_1576347704364_3290">hie </ab></add> beẏ vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_527_line_1576347708582_3295">geleite </ab></add> hat / er ſey <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> hie oder geſte / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l29">vver recht darcʒu hat / dem <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir den gern <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l30">vnd wo vvir ew in den oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb vnd freuntſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l31"><expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir wıllig etc / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_527_r1l32">Anno etc duodecimo $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_527" id="263r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erfford </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Hansen, seligen, und Berlds,
                        seins prüders, von <expan>Goszerstete<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburge<ex>r,</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und lassen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz wir nichts hie erfaren
                                <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan>, das der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Hans von
                            <expan>Goszerstete<ex>n</ex></expan>, selig, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, hie gelassen hab
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> etwievil waits, der hie auf dem weithause
                        ligt; und den mag auch <expan>nyemand<ex>en</ex></expan> hie bekümern noch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pieten,</expan>
<expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> der wait <add>hie</add> bey uns
                            <add>geleite</add> hat, er sey <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> hie oder
                        geste, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wer recht darczu hat, dem
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir den gern
                            <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen. Und wo wir ew in den oder
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und freuntschaft
                                <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n,</ex></expan> des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli anno etc. duodecimo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
